{"tid":606543,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[癡撚線] 有冇人試過碌ig story見到啲咁嘅嘢","createTime":"2018-03-26T14:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T14:18:49.000Z","uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c5100d681ec987bc9eccf922eeee75e1341c43b4","tid":606543,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:29:40.000Z","msg":"依家ig被Suckerburg買咗之後就改頭換面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇咗地圖mode仲改埋feed嘅玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都算 唔係呢個post嘅重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家啲廣告愈出愈多，連story都要攝一兩個廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啱啱就見到呢個廣告。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於事出突然而我又慣性想skip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係cap到一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成條片冇露點啊剩，淨係un下un下<br />\n似係大陸樣唔敢肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都好癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n㩒佢icon又冇profile google都搵唔到啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問有冇巴絲知可以點約到呢啲date<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0057babc3c9412632fb6dd397f46c3ca864f0c08","tid":606543,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:30:49.000Z","msg":"仲想問 點解人在外國仲會見到啲大陸廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見其他廣告都幾local下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff236c09cb76e1aea5e270046c1025f9691d2034","tid":606543,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03